Best Free CBR Reader Software for Windows

Comica

Comica is primarily a free software which contains collection of free comic books and it is also one of the best CBR reader.

Roboreader

Roboreader can be used to view most of the popular files including CBR file.

ComicRack

ComicRack is a multiple CBR files reader software which can also convert files in between various file formats.

CBR Reader

CBR Reader is one the best CBR reader software which supports almost all type of comic book file formats to read.

GonVisor

GonVisor is a quality image, eBook, magazine and CBR viewer software. It provides many quality and useful viewing features. 

Comic Seer

Comic Seer can view or read more than one CBR file by opening them in multiple tabs using this software.

MangaMeeya

MangaMeeya can open CBR files in dual page mode.

NTComic CBR Reader

NTComic CBR Reader can open two images from a CBR file simultaneously to read.

CoView

CoView is unique because it works only in full  screen mode.
